Package com.forst.lukas.pibe.fragment

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppFilterFragment
    Fragment which provide simple application filter.
    DeviceInfoFragment
    Fragment with main device info.
    HomeFragment
    Fragment with main screen displayed after start of the application.
    LogFragment
    Fragment class which provide Log screen with two main elements - whole notification log and current present notification.
    PermissionFragment
    Fragment with permission text, that application need access to the notification permission.
    SettingsFragment
    Fragment with application settings and connection to the server.
